Proficiency in Python and SQL, with familiarity with cloud-based data platforms such as AWS, Azure, or GCP;
Confidence managing complexity and ambiguity with autonomy;
Strong interpersonal skills and comfort communicating with non-technical audiences;
Curiosity, creativity, and a genuine drive to keep learning.
Solid English proficiency (B2+).




👉 Do you meet most of the position requirements? Then grab this opportunity and apply now! 🤩💪




✨ What we offer:

